    Axis, CalibratedAxis, TypedAxis

    public class ChapmanRichardsAxis
extends Variable3Axis
    Implement an axis that uses Chapman and Richards method of scaling. This axis based on ImageJ 1.x's CurveFitter algorithm.
    Author:
    Barry DeZonia
